vencimientoAnticipado.descripcion:
Check field "Y / N" in which it is informed if a contract can be expired early. The calculation logic is as follows:
o Criterion 1: In the first half of the life of the loan (calculated based on the formalization date of the contract and its natural maturity date), if the unpaid principal is equal to or greater than 3% of the amount of initial capital granted (Formalized) or if the unpaid installments are equal to or greater than 12 (based on the installments issued in total or partially unpaid).
o Criterion 2: If it is in the second half of the life of the loan, the unpaid principal is equal to or greater than the initial 7% or there are 15 or more unpaid installments.
